review: From my first interaction of confirming pregnancy to my delivery, Dr. Prasanna was always there. She is professional, approachable and answers all your questions. She played a major role at the time of my delivery. Thank you doctor.
Nice to meet mam..Prasanna mam is very good docter and  she was treat very friendly..I am satisfied  to consult her..thank you mam
Thank you Doc for being available on the weekends and i really appreciate your time. I recommend to all

I visited doctor on 1st, she wrote scan, cbp,cue and asked to meet again next day. I informed doctor that I get time in evening so doctor said to come after 7.  Today I called her assistant she asked me to send reports on WhatsApp i sent the cbp and told her that doctor asked to meet again in evening with scan. She said she will check with dr & get back I waited & called again there was no response then I called again from another no she answered & said dr is busy in surgery & cannot meet me in evening 7-9 slot bcz assistant was not answering I went into practo again to book appointment and doctor was accepting fresh appointments between 7-9 slot so basically they don't want to take the existing patient revisit
It was good experience. ****** *** ************* *** spent sufficient time for diagnosis. She was patient in listening to us and gave additional information to solve the problem.

I had taken appointment for my friend and we have visited Oxy Medical Centres. Dr. Prasanna was very nice with us and did the check up, once the check up was completely he had provided the treatment. All thing was great only for us in the clinic and we are fully satisfied with him. So I would like to recommend this for my family also.
